                     <interp inst="t18361024-2306-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18361024-cd-59" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18361024-2306-offence-1 t18361024-cd-59"></join>12th of October</rs>, a gelding, value £9., the property of <persName id="t18361024-name-427" type="victimName">
